    "He graduated from Princeton University in 1929 <em>magna cum laude</em>, a classmate and friend of John D. Rockefeller III (1906-1978).": [],
    "After a year of post-graduate work, Roberts accepted a position at the Pennsylvania Museum of art (now the Philadelphia Museum of Art), then under the directorship of <a href=\"/kimballf\">Fiske Kimball</a>.": [],
